divs: Sighting DetailsDuring our evening walk, we (three individuals) noticed two rapidly moving objects traveling overhead at about 20,000 to 25,000 feet. Both objects were brightly lit and traveling in tandem by a distance of about a quarter mile. No sound was present and no coloured or blinking lights. We frequently see aircraft and these two objects were not airplanes, nor were they satellites.
Summary: Two rapidly moving objects in tandem seperated by quarter of a mile.
